### Problem Description

The endpoint /_transform/{transform_id}/_schedule_now does not run instantly a continuous transform to process data.

### Steps to Reproduce

1. Create a continuous transform

```
{
  "source": {
    "index": "source_index"
  },
  "dest": {
    "index": "dest_index"
  },
  "pivot": {
    "group_by": {
      "term": {
        "terms": {
          "field": "field1"
        }
      },
      "classNumber": {
        "terms": {
          "field": "field2"
        }
      },
      "language": {
        "terms": {
          "field": "field3"
        }
      }
    },
    "aggregations": {
      "last_updated": {
        "max": {
          "field": "ingested"
        }
      }
    }
  },
  "sync": {
    "time": {
      "field": "ingested",
      "delay": "2s"
    }
  },
  "frequency": "10m"
}
```

2. Start the transform calling the endpoint /_transform/{transform_id}/_start
3. Add new documents to the source index
4. Perform a POST request to the endpoint _transform/{transform_id}/_schedule_now

The destination index is not updated with the new documents as the transform does not run.

